==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Professed
<hw>Pro*fessed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Openly declared,
avowed, acknowledged, or claimed; <as>as, a <ex>professed</ex> foe; a
<ex>professed</ex> tyrant; a <ex>professed</ex>
Christian.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The professed</b></col> <fld>(R. C. Ch.)</fld> <cd>, a
certain class among the Jesuits bound by a special vow. See the note
under <er>Jesuit</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Professedly</ent>⟦br⟧
